List Segment Efforts

Source: R/get_segment_efforts.R
get_segment_efforts.Rd

Returns a set of the authenticated athlete's segment efforts for a given segment. Requires subscription.

Usage

get_segment_efforts(
  segment_id,
  start_date_local = NULL,
  end_date_local = NULL,
  per_page = 30,
  scope = "activity:read",
  client = strava_client()
)

Arguments

segment_id

The identifier of the segment.

start_date_local

ISO 8601 formatted date time.

end_date_local

ISO 8601 formatted date time.

per_page

Number of items per page. Defaults to 30.

scope

Authorization scope.

client

Strava client. By default, assumes you have client credentials stored in your .Renviron file.

Examples

if (FALSE) {
  get_segment_efforts(10561790)
}
